prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, dynamic comic book style. A hilarious action scene where Lao Lao and Jordan, transformed into illustrated superhero characters based on the reference photo, are in a chaotic, brightly colored kitchen. Lao Lao is the main hero, wearing her blue sweatshirt and a confident, playful smirk. She skillfully balances a tray holding two large, overflowing boba milk tea cups while simultaneously using a dog leash to wrangle two small, adorable dogs (a fluffy Corgi and a happy Shiba Inu) who are causing a playful ruckus. Jordan, in his brown hoodie, is in the background, comically slipping on a banana peel, mid-air, with a classic "Whoa!" expression and motion lines trailing behind him. The background is filled with comic book elements like "KAPOW!" and "ZOOM!" sound effect bubbles, Halftone dot patterns, and Kirby Krackle energy effects. The entire scene is vibrant with bold outlines and a saturated color palette. Centered in the middle of the scene, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday to my favorite superhero, Lao Lao!". Flat 2D artwork for printing.
